query: SELECT    SUBSTR(x.DLRA_DIV_CDE,1,1) AS DLRA_DIV_CDE, x.DLRA_ACCT_CDE AS DLRA_ACCT_CDE FROM    DW_ADM.DLRA_DELR_ACCT_D  x  WHERE  x.DLRA_ACCT_TYPE_CDE ='RTLR' AND x.DLRA_ACCT_STS='Active' OR x.DLRA_ACCT_TYPE_CDE ='RTLR' AND x.DLRA_ACCT_STS='Inactive' OR x.DLRA_ACCT_TYPE_CDE ='RTLR' AND x.DLRA_ACCT_STS='Independent' OR x.DLRA_ACCT_TYPE_CDE ='RTLR' AND x.DLRA_ACCT_STS='Temporary' OR x.DLRA_ACCT_TYPE_CDE ='BULK' AND x.DLRA_ACCT_STS='Temporary' OR x.DLRA_ACCT_TYPE_CDE ='BULK' AND x.DLRA_ACCT_STS='Inactive' OR x.DLRA_ACCT_TYPE_CDE ='BULK' AND x.DLRA_ACCT_STS='Active' OR x.DLRA_ACCT_TYPE_CDE ='CNTR' AND x.DLRA_ACCT_STS='Temporary'
